Parliament, Wednesday, 15 August 2018 – The Portfolio Committee on Higher Education and Training is to be briefed by the National Student Financial Aid Scheme (NSFAS) on funding challenges and backlogs for the current financial year. The Department of Higher Education and Training, Universities SA and student formations will make submissions at the meeting. Details of the meeting are as follows: Date : 16 August 2018 Venue : Old Assembly Chamber (Parliament) Time : 09h00 – 14h00 ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE PORTFOLIO COMMITTEE ON HIGHER EDUCATION AND TRAINING, MS CONNIE SEPTEMBER. For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the Committee’s Media Officer: Name: Sibongile Maputi
	Parliamentary Communication Services
	Tel: 021 403 8138
	Cell: 081 052 6060
